-- Santiago Retail Sales Rose 5.5% in April From Year Earlier
-- B y   R a n d a l l   W o o d s
-- 2012-05-28T15:38:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-28/santiago-retail-sales-rose-5-5-in-april-from-year-earlier.html
Retail sales in Santiago rose 5.5
percent in April from the same month last year,  Chile ’s chamber
of commerce, known as CNC, said in a report today.  The government’s National Statistics Institute is scheduled
to publish retail sales data for the country on May 31.  To contact the reporter on this story:
